<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Blog Layout</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset & Base Styles */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      color: #333;
    }

    /* Header Styles */
    header {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      padding: 1rem 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header nav a {
      color: white;
      margin: 0 1rem;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    header nav a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* Main Content Styles */
    main {
      max-width: 800px; /* Centered content width */
      margin: 2rem auto; /* Centering with auto margins */
      padding: 1rem;
      background-color: white;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    /* Article Styles */
    article h2 {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: #4CAF50;
    }

    article p {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    /* Footer Styles */
    footer {
      background-color: #333;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem 0;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      main {
        margin: 1rem;
        padding: 0.5rem;
      }

      header nav a {
        display: block;
        margin: 0.5rem 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>My Blog</h1>
    <nav>
      <a href="#home">Home</a>
      <a href="#about">About</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <article>
      <h2>Blog Post Title</h2>
      <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Proin vitae arcu libero.</p>
    </article>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2024 My Blog. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>